{"id":306397,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-湖南江华县数百瑶族库区移民围堵县政府/","date":"2013-07-30T10:18:30Z","modified":"2013-07-30T10:18:30Z","title":"维权网 | 湖南江华县数百瑶族库区移民围堵县政府抗议安置不公（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日，湖南省江华瑶族自治县涔天河水库瑶族移民数百人游行示威，围堵了当地县政府，抗议移民安置不公。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年，涔天河水库扩建工程开工建设，工程涉及移民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>万多户，当地政府逼迫、欺骗移民签字，只给移民每年每人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">400</span><span>元的土地流转收益，承诺的移民安置小区也迟迟不见踪影，村民怀疑移民资金被政府贪污。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span>由于对库区补偿偏低、后期扶持力度不够等原因，目前民族地区库区和库区移民生产生活存在许多困难，甚至吃饭都成了问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rS_oW_qxeBk/UfeGnC2vrGI/AAAAAAAAmFM/9Kxpr_czCl4/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"275\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-rS_oW_qxeBk/UfeGnC2vrGI/AAAAAAAAmFM/9Kxpr_czCl4/s400/1.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-n-THDCtAGj4/UfeGnjeSPwI/AAAAAAAAmFU/eaOu54zHmmw/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"276\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-n-THDCtAGj4/UfeGnjeSPwI/AAAAAAAAmFU/eaOu54zHmmw/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vD-Gw_XIwkc/UfeGotwLTQI/AAAAAAAAmFc/WCi9xOZ0gi0/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"277\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vD-Gw_XIwkc/UfeGotwLTQI/AAAAAAAAmFc/WCi9xOZ0gi0/s400/3.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.l